<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <script src="https://use.fontawesome.com/8feb4bfacc.js"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Kurale" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../public/styles.css">
    <title>Meal Planner | Welcome</title>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <h1><a href="/"><i class="fa fa-cutlery" aria-hidden="true"></i>Meal Planner</h1></a>
                <nav><a href="index/add-meal">Add Meal</a></nav>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main class="table">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <form class="add-meal" method="POST" action="/index/view-meal/:meal">
            <h2>Add Meal</h2>
                <div>
                    <p> Are you tired of having to plan what to eat three times a day but don't want to pay an expensive meal service
                    to deliver meals to your door? With our meal planner you no longer have to worry! You can upload your meals
                    to Meal Planner and choose your meals for breakfast, lunch, dinner and even all three! Gone are the days
                    of wasting time making useless decisions. Meal Planner has you covered! </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <select name="meal" style="flex-basis: 100%; height: 40px;">
                    <option value="breakfast">Breakfast</option>
                    <option value="lunch">Lunch</option>
                    <option value="dinner">Dinner</option>
                    <option value="day">Full Day!</option>
                    </select>
                    <button>Submit</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <p>Meal Planner Â© 2017</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>